</p><a href="http://diarioeconomico.sapo.pt/edicion/diarioeconomico/edicion_impresa/destaque/pt/desarrollo/1191495.html"><img src="http://i.s.sl.pt/6456c683f7db1c57b3babe6dfb78e112.jpg" width="220" height="160" border="0"/></a>]]></description>
